summary: I don’t know if y’all internationals realise but like to anyone who was young in the 1990’s in Britain, “Angels” is just a...
body: I don’t know if y’all internationals realise but like to anyone who was young in the 1990’s in Britain, “Angels” is just a staple classic. Every single person knows the words and you won’t catch a single person under 40 who won’t sing along… and Taylor said she wanted to see how loud the Stadium could get if she played a song ‘everyone here knows’. To have a whole stadium singing such a throwback from childhood so loudly that you couldn’t even really hear Taylor or Robbie really was something.

body:
First concert!

So… Can we talk about how impressed my non-swiftie boyfriend was with the show? He knew every song except for Fifteen and he said that everyone should go to a @taylorswift show even if they don’t like Taylor’s music. It was his first Taylor Swift’s concert and my 4th and pretty much one of the best days of my life!!!!

Since we’re engineers, he was also so impressed with the light-up bracelets 😂😂😂
